    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Photobiomodulation Induced by 670 nm Light Ameliorates MOG35-55 Induced EAE in Female C57BL/6 Mice: A Role for Remediation of Nitrosative Stress]]></Value>
    </articleTitle>
